      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my chest is feeling kinda tight and burning kinda bad right now. i had a huge pizza dinner earlier so i think it might just be bad heartburn but it's also kinda creeping down my left arm. should i just take some Tums and wait it out or is that a bad idea?",
