      "content": "idk i dont really wanna go to the er if i can help it, it's always so expensive and the wait is crazy. i've had this happen a few times when i eat too much greasy food. i'm pretty sure it's just the pizza. if i take a double dose of an antacid it should help, right? it's probably just gas or something.",
