      "content": "wait, a walk? i feel kinda lightheaded and dizzy when i move around, so i'd rather just stay on the couch. if it's just indigestion the antacid should work eventually. i've got some extra strength stuff here, can i just take 3 of them at once to get ahead of the pain? it's better than sitting here feeling like this.",
